![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7c8fcae1-f3ef-4cc4-a0f7-ef14523b77ec/13029.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_ALEXA BLISS DEF. PIPER NIVEN_**
    

Post Match, Secret HERvice attack Alexa, Charlotte runs in but it's not enough. HERvice stands tall

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/859048eb-9a82-42c2-996d-149a535ef18a/13030.jpg?format=original)

Jade Cargill is trying to get a Women's Championship match when Nia Jax interrupted and pissed off Tiffany Stratton. Seems like we're heading to Nia vs Tiffy vs Jade.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e8bce2dd-ac91-4f77-afaa-b3188abb3b1c/13053.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_MELO DON'T MIZ DEF. FRAXIOM_**
    

This was a GREAT match that even saw the Miz break up a pinfall by using Frazier as a springboard to DDT Axiom

Melo was going to get the win in his hometown but the Miz blind tags him and steals it for himself.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ce72acaf-20fd-4b5a-a51a-c1c7526960b5/13057.jpg?format=original)

Drew McIntyre cuts a great promo saying he didn't attack Cody Rhodes. Cody Rhodes attacked him first. Drew explains that Cody was thinking about putting him through a table during the tag match with Cena and Logan Paul so Drew was taking him out in defense.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2780ec9c-cb43-4840-96ea-f47265318698/13058.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/221a7789-354d-4e6f-bf47-0d467a3c7c81/13068.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_STREET PROFITS DEF. DIY_**
    

Pretty quick match that saw Candice LeRae get involved but it wasn't enough to take down the Profits.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/62eb571d-cbf2-4bb3-9589-b45c566eba07/13070.jpg?format=original)

Carmelo Hayes tried to ask Nick Aldis what he has to do for a United States Title match

The Miz cut him off again, and Melo Don’t Miz now have a match next week against The Motor City Machine Guns

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b35d2157-fc67-4633-9ea8-82ff8bf2cfef/13072.jpg?format=original)

R-Truth is happy and trying to talk about John Cena when Aleister Black shows up and R Truth shifts back into Ron Killings.

Ron Killings vs Aleister Black is set for next week

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/02944e1e-038e-4f09-94f6-2fe22739bcf5/13073.jpg?format=original)

